name: Stars Bamboo Bracelet
description:
This bracelet consists of 9 black bamboo tiles that have each been covered with a black and white stars pattern. Each tile has been triple sealed. The bracelet is stretchy so it will fit nearly any wrist. I can always add or delete a tile if necessary. Each tile measures 1 1/2 inches tall by 3/4 inches wide and 1/8 inch thick.

Although I strive to make each piece of jewelry durable so that it may last for many, many years, please take care of them. I wouldn't shower or swim with this piece nor would I set it on fire.  All items are handmade by me in my northside Chicago apartment.

name: Cowboy Puzzle Piece Pendant
description:
This necklace is comprised of a puzzle piece reclaimed and reworked into a very fabulous pendant. It has been sealed with resin to ensure its longevity.

The pendant measures 1 3/4" long and 1 1/4" wide. It comes on a silver-tone chain and clasp. The chain measures 16" but it can be adjusted.

All of my items are handmade in my Chicago apartment.  Although I strive to make each piece of jewelry durable so that it may last for many, many years, please take care of them. I wouldn't shower or swim with this piece nor would I set it on fire.

name: Put the money in your pocket Bamboo Necklace
description:
This is necklace has the phrase, "Put the money in your pocket." from a 1950's children's early reader. The white paper was placed on a black bamboo tile. The pendant measures almost 4" across and a 1/4" wide. The necklace is 14" long end to end and hits slightly below the collar bone. I could make the chain longer if needed.

This necklace has been triple sealed but I wouldn't swim, take a shower or set it on fire.
